parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver seat mounting can cause the seat to break loose, rock back and forth, or even collapse, which can lead to loss of control, accidents, or injuries.

or collapses; the seat mounting bolts or welds break or crack; the seat frame tears or breaks around the mounting nut.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A faulty power mirror switch can cause a fire inside the door, potentially spreading to other parts of the vehicle and posing a risk to occupants.
